## 🔧 Implementation Guidelines

### Documentation Quality Standards
- **Clarity:** Turkish autism education context always considered
- **Technical Accuracy:** Include specific commands, file paths, and metrics
- **Success Tracking:** Before/after comparisons for all improvements
- **User Impact:** Always document how changes benefit children with autism

### Proactive Documentation Triggers
- **Feature Completion:** Auto-update TODO and PRD
- **Error Resolution:** Auto-create fail-report with solution
- **Performance Milestone:** Update README and relevant docs
- **Test Coverage Achievement:** Document in TODO with metrics

### Integration with Development Workflow
- **Real-time Updates:** Documentation updated during conversation
- **Cross-referencing:** Link related documents and achievements
- **Version Control:** Track documentation evolution with platform development
- **Accessibility Focus:** Maintain autism-friendly language and clear explanations

